      "content": "I hear how much pain you're in right now, and it takes real courage to admit that you feel like a burden. Please know that your feelings are valid, but they don't define your worth as a parent or a person. You are not a problem; you are a human navigating a very difficult time, and those struggles don't mean you're failing your kids.\n\nYou deserve support without judgment, and reaching out here is already a brave step toward finding relief. If you're open to it, I can share some gentle resources or just listen as we talk through what's weighing on you. You don't have to carry this alone.",
